description:

Will my engineering brain actually help me make things better — or just create a bigger mess? Come hang out, watch the chaos unfold, and maybe help me figure out how to stop everything from catching fire.

title: The Factory Must Grow: Factorio Madness | Engineezy Live ep.4

author: Engineezy
description:
Necessary fix to an unnecessary problem…
•••
Im working on a project with thousands of these little colorful marbles, and it has a tendency to spew them all over my floor.  So after spending another 45 minutes picking them all up by hand, I had a better idea. Inspired by a driving range picker, the wheels snag the marbles, and the little combs kick them out into the basket.  At the very least I can save my back a bit while I contemplate my future project choices.
•••
Stay tuned for this project, its one of my favorite ones so far!
•••
#engineering #invention #mechanicalengineering #3dprinting
title: Necessary Solution to an Unnecessary Problem
